Description: Ensurge Micropower ASA (Ensurge), is a Norway-based microbattery manufacturing company. The Company produces rechargeable solid-state lithium batteries (SSLB) for diverse applications. Its electrical characteristics are compatible with other rechargeable lithium batteries such as lithium ion. This enables the Ensurge Microbattery to be used with prevalent power and battery management systems and ensures easy integration into existing and new products. The Company uses a solid-state electrolyte instead of the liquid layer of lithium-ion batteries, making it safer to use. In addition, solid-state chemistry affords multiple valuable features that allow their customers to build better products.
